OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright but with a few spots of
OL,6,Flight rain not to be ruled out, though
OL,7,Fmany places staying dry until patchy
OL,8,Flight rain spreads across from the
OL,9,Fsouthwest late afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRather cloudy with a few
OL,12,Fspots of mainly light rain, perhaps
OL,13,Fturning more persistent in the east at
OL,14,Ftimes, while clearer spells develop
OL,15,Ffurther west.
OL,16,
